 Project Summary  
This project is a  created to present my background, skills, education, and web projects.  

It demonstrates front-end development ability using HTML and Tailwind CSS (CLI) 
The site includes a video background, smooth transitions, responsive layout, and a fixed interactive navigation bar.  

